<h1>Reports samples</h1>

<p>A <a href="monthly.grd" target="_blank">GNUe 
Reports Defintion</a> file (.grd) is used by 
the GNUe Reports engine to create an 
<a href="monthly.xml" target="_blank">XML</a> output file, 
which is then transformed using normal XML 
tools into the required format, such as 
<a href="monthly.html" target="_blank">HTML</a>
(Hyper-Text Mark-up Language) or even just 
<a href="monthly.txt" target="_blank">plain text</a>.</p>
